26#include "config.h"
27#include "CachedResourceHandle.h"
28
29#include "CachedResource.h"
30
31namespace WebCore {
32
33CachedResourceHandleBase::CachedResourceHandleBase()
34 : m_resource(nullptr)
35{
36}
37
38CachedResourceHandleBase::CachedResourceHandleBase(CachedResource* resource)
39 : m_resource(resource)
40{
41 if (m_resource)
42 m_resource->registerHandle(this);
43}
44
45CachedResourceHandleBase::CachedResourceHandleBase(const CachedResourceHandleBase& other)
46 : m_resource(other.m_resource)
47{
48 if (m_resource)
49 m_resource->registerHandle(this);
50}
51
52CachedResourceHandleBase::~CachedResourceHandleBase()
53{
54 if (m_resource)
55 m_resource->unregisterHandle(this);
56}
57
58void CachedResourceHandleBase::setResource(CachedResource* resource)
59{
60 if (resource == m_resource)
61 return;
62 if (m_resource)
63 m_resource->unregisterHandle(this);
64 m_resource = resource;
65 if (m_resource)
66 m_resource->registerHandle(this);
67}
68
69}
